.TH CMD2MOT 1 "2026-05-18" "f9dasm 1.83" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
cmd2mot \- convert FLEX9 binary (.CMD) files to Motorola S\-records
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cmd2mot
.RI [ \-out
.IR file ]
.I file.cmd
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cmd2mot
reads a FLEX9 binary
.RB ( .CMD )
file and emits the equivalent Motorola S\-record stream, suitable for
loading into ROM programmers or as input to
.BR mot2bin (1).
.PP
It is shipped as a companion utility to
.BR f9dasm (1)
for round\-tripping FLEX9 binaries between dump formats.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-out " file"
Write the S\-record output to
.IR file
instead of standard output.
.SH EXAMPLES
Convert
.I prog.cmd
to
.IR prog.s19 :
.IP
.B cmd2mot \-out prog.s19 prog.cmd
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR f9dasm (1),
.BR hex2bin (1),
.BR mot2bin (1)
.SH AUTHORS
Part of the
.B f9dasm
suite by Arto Salmi, Hermann Seib, Colin Bourassa, and Rainer Buchty.
